                        <interp inst="t18390916-name-1081" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN BOLT</persName>
                  </hi>. My wife called me—I saw the prisoner in the shop—my wife collared him—he got from her—I ran after him—this is a watch I had to repair—I can swear to it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
