                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant D</hi> 4.) I was in Stafford street, and heard the cry of "Stop thief"—I saw Bolt following the pri<lb></lb>soner—I stopped him—he said he had done nothing—I took him back—Mrs. Bolt gave me the watch, and showed me where he had laid it down.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I went into the shop—the watch was lying down in the place—I never unhooked it at all.</p>
